Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:49.34,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Kono yo no doko ka de hikatte 'ru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:49.34,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}En algún lugar de este mundo brillan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.17,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Soitsu mitsuke ni yuko ze BOY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.17,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}¡Vamos a salir a buscarlas, muchacho!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.11,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Yokai henge mo buttobashi{\i0}
